+# Invoice template interchange (ALEYA ↔ Aleya Invoicing)
+
+See the canonical contract in the ALEYA repository:
+
+`docs/invoice/TEMPLATE_INTERCHANGE_CONTRACT.md`
+
+## Import
+
+```
+POST /api/integrations/invoice-templates/import
+{ "template": { ...aleya.invoiceTemplate }, "activate": true }
+```
+
+## Active template
+
+```
+GET /api/integrations/invoice-templates/active
+DELETE /api/integrations/invoice-templates/active
+```
+
+When an active template is present, `GET /api/invoices/:id/pdf` renders through
+`generateTemplatedInvoicePdfBuffer` instead of the legacy fixed PDFKit layout.
